<li>Clary, Isabelle. "<a href="http://coweb.sv.publicus.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20070219/PRINTSUB/702190711" class="external text" title="http://coweb.sv.publicus.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20070219/PRINTSUB/702190711" rel="nofollow">Wall Street Spreading the Word on Options -- Derivative Instruments Now Being Pushed as Source of Better Returns, not Just for Hedging</a>." <i>Pensions &amp; Investments</i>. (February 19, 2007).</li>
<li>Hadi, Mohammed. "Buy-Write Strategy Could Help in Sideways Market." <i>Wall Street Journal</i>. (April 29, 2006) pg. B5.</li>
