<li>Tergesen, Anne. <a href="http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/01_21/b3733128.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/01_21/b3733128.htm" rel="nofollow">"Taking Cover with Covered Calls."</a> <i>Business Week</i>, (May 21, 2001), pp. 132.</li>
